</li>
<li><p>Microsoft Excel 98 for Macintosh:<br/>
<a href="http://www.microsoft.com/mac/downloads.aspx?pid=download&amp;location=/mac/download/office98/pptxlmacro.xml&amp;secid=20&amp;ssid=20&amp;flgnosysreq=false" data-linktype="external">http://www.microsoft.com/mac/downloads.aspx?pid=download&amp;location=/mac/DOWNLOAD/OFFICE98/pptxlmacro.xml&amp;secid=20&amp;ssid=20&amp;flgnosysreq=False</a></p>
</li>
